🔷 2. RECORD VIEW ENGINE STRUCTURE (CATEGORIES)

Categories is a single-section record view.
It is more complex than UOM due to its 5 UOM unit selectors but follows
the exact same structural pattern.

Structure:

RecordView: Category
  → FieldSection: General (PrimaryRow: Category)
      Fields: name, sendUnitId, stockUnitId, coverageAvailableUnitId,
              itemCoverageUnitId, serviceUnitId
      Actions: Save, Delete

Why This Matters:
* All 5 unit selectors live in a single section
* Save replaces the full section snapshot
* Delete is guarded by domain rules at the application layer

