🧠 5. DOMAIN LAYER (Business Rules — Source of Truth)

Target location: packages/domain/src/flooring/categories/

delete-rules.ts:

  type CategoryDeleteLinkState = {
    productLinks: number
  }

  isCategoryDeleteBlocked(state: CategoryDeleteLinkState): boolean
    return state.productLinks > 0

  getCategoryDeleteBlockedMessage(state: CategoryDeleteLinkState): string
    if state.productLinks > 0:
      return "This category is linked to products and cannot be deleted"
    return ""

name-rules.ts:

  normalizeCategoryNameForUniqueness(value: string): string
    return value.trim().toLowerCase()

  isCategoryNameConflict(exists: boolean): boolean
    return exists

  assertCategoryNameAvailable(exists: boolean): void
    if isCategoryNameConflict(exists):
      throw CategoryExecutionError({ code: "CATEGORY_NAME_CONFLICT", status: 409, field: "name" })

Rules:
* ❗ Domain has no Prisma imports
* ❗ Domain has no HTTP imports
* ❗ Domain functions are pure — input in, decision out

